About This Company
Mondragon Educacion Internacional (MEI, Spain) and Wintec (New Zealand) are leading providers of international technical education and are working in partnership to manage a cluster of 3 colleges in the coastal region of Tabuk as one of the International Operators.You can find more information about our project in the following webpage: www.saudicollegejobs.comYou can find more information about Mondragon and Wintec in:www.mondragon-corporation.comwww.wintec.ac.nzwww.saudicollegejobs.com
